snippet.title: Thomas & Friends - On Site with Thomas - Original Music Test
snippet.description:
Thomas & Friends - On Site with Thomas - Original Music Test
Toegevoegd door Bladez636 laatste januari
Video from summer 2013, I had the urge to do some of these. The On Site with Thomas saga are afterall part of the original series - despite being released in 2006; they were made alongside Season 6 in 2002 and filmed with 35mm instead of digital cameras like Seasons 8-on. So it's only fitting to try and do some tests with original music by Mike O'Donnell & Junior Campbell. Ultimately the whole thing will be done in time for all of them; full episodes.
